




     killipcs

     NAME
            killipcs - release ipc resources owned by user

     SYNOPSIS
            killipcs

     DESCRIPTION
	    This shell script will remove all ipc resources owned
	    by the user.  Its purpose is simply to save the user
	    the trouble of typing in the id of each ipc resource
	    with the ipcrm command.

     SEE ALSO
	    ipcs(1), ipcrm(1), msgctl(2), msgget(2), msgop(2), semctl(2),
            semget(2), semop(2), shmctl(2), shmget(2), shmop(2)

